                <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 block-right">
                    <div class="section-head pb-100">
                        <h2><i class="fa fa-crosshairs"></i> Alumni</h2>
                        <a href="../alumni_form" target="_blank" class="join_btn">Join As Alumni</a>
<a href="alumni-committee-members" target="_blank" class="join_btn">Alumni Committee Members</a>
<a href="alumni-testimonial" target="_blank" class="join_btn">Alumni Testimonial</a>

<p>BBIT Alumni Association has been formed on May 9, 2015 to foster a sense of belonging towards the college among the former students and enable them to carry forward the vision and mission of the college in their personal and professional lives as well as to create and make use of a network of alumni members who can contribute to the growth and development of the college as well as help create successful careers for the students.</p>

<h4 class="contact-heading back-lightbl"><b>Roles & Functions</b></h4>

<ul>
 <li>To build profiles of successful alumni of the college to serve as inspiration for the students and faculty.</li>
 <li>To build a database of all alumni members with their contact details and maintain a regular dialogue with them through emails or newsletters;</li>
 <li>To carry out an exit survey of the students for obtaining their feedback on their experiences, which can be used for carrying out continuous improvement in academic and administrative practices;</li>
 <li>To carry out an exit survey of teachers leaving the college for obtaining their feedback on their experiences, which can be used for carrying out continuous improvement in academic and administrative practices;</li>
 <li>To organize workshops/training programs which could benefit the alumni members in their life goals;</li>
 <li>To establish web interface pages in social media such as Face book, twitter, LinkedIn, google+, etc. to facilitate greater interaction among the alumni members and with the current faculty members.</li></ul>

<h4 class="contact-heading back-lightorn"><b>Alumni Engagement</b></h4>

<ul>
 <li>Few Alumni Members were added in the reconstruction of the Internal Quality Assurance Committee (IQAC) of the college on 31st May, 2021.</li><li>Series of Special Webinars were conducted by the Alumni for the final year students of 2021 Pass Out Batch.</li><li>Webinar on "Session with the Alumni" for the freshers on 7th Oct, 2020.</li><li>A football match was held between ex-champions' vs present champion team of BBIT on 29th Feb, 2020.</li><li>Dates of Alumni General Body Meets & Reunions:</li></ul><p>Sun, 24 Nov 2013; Sun 04 May, 2014; Sun, 23 Nov, 2014; Sun, 03 May, 2015; Sun, 08 Nov, 2015; Sun 31 Jul, 2016; Sun, 18 Dec, 2016; Sun, 06 Aug, 2017; Sat, 29 Dec, 2018; Fri, 20 Dec, 2019; Sat, 29 Feb, 2020.</p><ul>
 <li>In the college cultural fest, there are lots of participation from the Alumni Association.</li>
 <li>Bengali Band “Ulto Shrot” performance led by Mr. Aquib Hayat of 2014-15.</li>
 <li>A Complete Alumni Football team of 12 members played a football tournament with our college’s current football team on the Sports Day during VERVE – 2016.</li>
 <li>A Networking site also has been created named <a href="http://bbit.almaconnect.com/">bbit.almaconnect.com</a>, where the passed out students can be in regular contact and share their whereabouts.</li>
</ul>
                        
                        
